==Trivia==
*His name is a pun based on the phrase'', ''"Hate us cause they ain't us", due to the fact he is wearing very rare and highly coveted equipment.
*Hatius Cosaintus appears to be wearing the [[Rune cane]], [[Briefcase]], [[3rd age platebody]], [[3rd age platelegs]], [[3rd age cloak]], [[Ranger boots]], [[Top hat & monocle]] and the [[Amulet of fury (or)]], which has an approximate value of {{Coins|{{GEP|Rune cane}}+{{GEP|Briefcase}}+{{GEP|3rd age platebody}}+{{GEP|3rd age platelegs}}+{{GEP|3rd age cloak}}+{{GEP|Ranger boots}}+{{GEP|Top hat & monocle}}+{{GEP|Amulet of fury}}+{{GEP|Fury ornament kit}}}}
*His out of place and unrealistic appearance has been criticised by players which led to the proposal to have him removed in [[Poll:Old School Content Poll 50: Models, Anims and More|Old School Content Poll #50: Models, Anims and More]]. However, with only 73.4% voting 'Yes', it failed the poll.

